                  %span.glyphicon.right{class: (p.personalised_theme? ? "glyphicon-ok" : "glyphicon-remove x")}
                  %span Theme/ logo on prints (artwork provided by customer)


    .heading-block.text-center.padding-top-50
      %h2 Need a little more?

      %hr/
      %span.margin-top-20.margin-bottom-20 Pick and choose from the extras to add a little more glam to your event
      %ul
        %li Host banners – Please enquire for more details
        %li Personalised booth skins
        %li 50 pounds per extra hour
        %li Large portraits for guest to leave a message and sign
